<div class="features-container">
  <header class="cd-header-home">
    <a href="/"><img id="logo" src="/assets/lytit-logotype.svg" style="width: 130px;" alt="Logo"></a>
    <a href="#0" class="cd-3d-nav-trigger-home">
      Menu
      <span></span>
    </a>
  </header> <!-- .cd-header -->

  <div class="cd-main-content">
    <div class="cd-product-intro">
      <h1>It's All About Places</h1>
      <p>A heat map, a social media search engine, and collective engagement are just some of the ways LYTiT will make you more locationally aware!</p>
      <div class="cd-triggers">
        <a class="btn">Coming Soon</a>
        <a href="#cd-product-tour" class="btn salmon" data-type="cd-tour">Show Me</a>
      </div>
    </div> <!-- cd-product-intro -->

    <div id="cd-product-tour">
      <ul>
        <li class="cd-single-item cd-active right-floater">
          <div class="cd-caption">
            <h2>Map</h2>
            <p>Lyts are assigned to places based on the amount and recency of social media activity. Search for a place or tap on a lyt to see what's happening there right now.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cd-image-container">
            <div>
              <div class="cd-phone-frame"></div>
              <div class="cd-image-wrapper">
                <img src="/assets/map@2x.png" data-video="/assets/map_with_touch" alt="Map Preview">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cd-single-item cd-not-visible cd-move-right left-floater">
          <div class="cd-caption">
            <h2>Pages</h2>
            <p>Search for a place or tap on a lyt to see what's happening there right now. Ping people on location for specific updates.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cd-image-container">
            <div>
              <div class="cd-phone-frame"></div>
              <div class="cd-image-wrapper">
                <img src="/assets/pages@2x.png" data-video="/assets/pages_with_touch" alt="Pages Preview">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cd-single-item cd-not-visible cd-move-right right-floater">
          <div class="cd-caption">
            <h2>Shake</h2>
            <p>All it takes is a shake to see what's going on at the place you are at and go Live!</p>
            <p style="margin-top: -40px">Going Live allows you to enlyten others about happenings at your location by responding to their pings.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cd-image-container">
            <div id="shake-feature">
              <div class="cd-phone-frame"></div>
              <div class="cd-image-wrapper">
                <img src="/assets/shake@2x.png" data-video="/assets/shake_with_touch" alt="Shake Preview">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cd-single-item cd-not-visible cd-move-right left-floater">
          <div class="cd-caption">
            <h2>Lists</h2>
            <p>Lists are a social way to discover places.
            <p style="margin-top: -40px">Create a list 
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cd-image-container">
            <div>
              <div class="cd-phone-frame"></div>
              <div class="cd-image-wrapper">
                <img src="/assets/lists@2x.png" data-video="/assets/lists_with_touch" alt="Lists Preview">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>

